{"tid":1243434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 堅尼地城現第一滴血","createTime":"2019-06-19T12:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T12:48:59.000Z","uid":105018,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"991d6a024b401b9bf8423cd09b5196e4f883fd41","tid":1243434,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"今次15隻警犬圍堵1隻野豬<br />\n過程中警犬保持克制 使用最低武力<br />\n使用0粒催淚彈<br />\n冇用盾牌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190619&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59736021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190619%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59736021&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=003166f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190619%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59736021&h=1be5eed4\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190619&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59736021</a><br />\n<br />\n一頭受傷的野豬，今日傍晚6時許闖入港鐵堅尼地城站內亂跑，牠腳部受傷血，站內出現一條條血路及腳印。野豬懷疑受驚，在大堂跑來跑去，其後走到升降機旁瑟縮一角，車站職員馬上暫停升降機運作，並圍起鐵馬堵塞通道，以免牠在站內亂竄。約15名警員接報趕至，架起兩層鐵馬陣戒備。<br />\n<br />\n讀者曾小姐表示，當時看見一隻野豬在車站大堂徘徊，而且不斷流血，狀甚驚慌，大批市民駐足圍觀。"},{"pid":"2b51675ae63ba5c8cae79763c2f432373e08da54","tid":1243434,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"[香港加油] 想喺聽日deadline前激勵下大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243430</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4bfbbb969b049ddb7a6906523eec21c041f23837","tid":1243434,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b51675ae63ba5c8cae79763c2f432373e08da54","tid":1243434,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"[香港加油] 想喺聽日deadline前激勵下大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243430</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:48:12.000Z","msg